ygData.messageBody:
Well I just got my SOW ring, Shiny Brass shield (Is it better then tower
shield?) and my travelr's back-pack! Wow I have 1 SOW ring, one cuthroat
ring and two onyx earrigns, man, I swing like a best couse my DEX is +2 and
I prob. run 3/5 faster! Plus with this travelr's back-pack it's great,
everything that goes into it gest reduced in weight super light! Wow, Now my
weight is around 60/98 This rocks! HeY I'll find oue where and who you get
the sSOW rings of off later tonight, I'm makeing my trip down to freeport so
WISH ME LUCK!!!

Dealan, Karana Server

All the Bloodstained armour (tunic, mantle and gloves) can be looted off the
Skeletal Knight who resides in unrest. He conned red to me at level 20. He
has a harm touch of 350hp. He always comes with an entourage when pulled. I
was in a level 25 party when we killed him, and our lead tank (a ranger)
nearly died in the battle (he had a slither of red left).

But I am VERY interested in the SoW ring. Only item that does the same
thing this ring you mentioned does, that I know off, are the journey man
boots. Looking at getting these with a level 30 party.
